{"word":"H947 - בּוּס - bûwç - boos - Loath","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בּוּס</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>bûwç"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>boos"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Loath"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"மிதி - வினைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to tread down, to reject, to trample down"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to tread down, to trample (used of warriors)"},{"paragraph":"2) used of rejection (figurative)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Polel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to tread down (in bad sense)"},{"paragraph":"2) to desecrate"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hithpolel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to tread"},{"paragraph":"2) to kick out"},{"paragraph":"a) used of infants' blind movements"},{"paragraph":"b) used of Jerusalem (figurative)"},{"paragraph":"d) (Hophal) to be trodden down"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>trample</i> (literally or figuratively): - loath, tread (down, under [foot]), be polluted."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2982 - יְבוּס - Yᵉbûwç - yeb-oos'/2982\">H2982</a>, <a href=\"#/H2983 - יְבוּסִי - Yᵉbûwçîy - yeb-oo-see'/2983\">H2983</a>, <a href=\"#/H4001 - מְבוּסָה - mᵉbûwçâh - meb-oo-saw'/4001\">H4001</a>, <a href=\"#/H8395 - תְּבוּסָה - tᵉbûwçâh - teb-oo-saw'/8395\">H8395</a>, <a href=\"#/H947 - בּוּס - bûwç - boos/947\">H947</a>"}]}